Package: areafoliar
Title: Leaf Area Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Paul Efren",
           family = "Santos Andrade",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paulefrens@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6635-0375"))
Description: An interface for the image processing program 'ImageJ', allowing digital image analysis for particle sizes and data management. This package includes a function to write an 'ImageJ' macro which is optimized for a leaf area analysis by default. This a version modified of LeafArea package(https://github.com/mattocci27/LeafArea), adding secondary functions to complete the data processing requirement of custom research project.
